    "raw": {
      "id": "51b5008d-a6ad-4e40-8cad-87ad2e72ac2f",
      "content": {
        "id": "51b5008d-a6ad-4e40-8cad-87ad2e72ac2f",
        "contentType": "VIDEO",
        "title": "Iran ceasefire market moves: bitcoin prices surge, Exxon stock falls",
        "description": "<p>Market Catalysts host Julie Hyman and Yahoo Finance Senior Reporter Brooke DiPalma take a look at some of Wednesday morning's <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\" class=\"link\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/markets/stocks/trending/\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\">trending tickers</a> and stories.</p><p>Bitcoin (<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\" class=\"link\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/BTC-USD/\" data-i13n=\"cpos:2;pos:1\">BTC-USD</a>) prices have surged to a three-week high on news of a ceasefire with Iran. The cryptocurrency is also rising after Iran requested that toll payments be made in crypto.</p><p>Energy stocks, including Exxon (<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\" class=\"link\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/XOM/\" data-i13n=\"cpos:3;pos:1\">XOM</a>), Chevron (<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\" class=\"link\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/CVX/\" data-i13n=\"cpos:4;pos:1\">CVX</a>), and Occidental (<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\" class=\"link\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/OXY/\" data-i13n=\"cpos:5;pos:1\">OXY</a>), are falling from the ceasefire news.</p><p>Cruise stocks, including Norwegian (<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\" class=\"link\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/NCLH/\" data-i13n=\"cpos:6;pos:1\">NCLH</a>), Royal Caribbean (<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\" class=\"link\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/RCL/\" data-i13n=\"cpos:7;pos:1\">RCL</a>), and Carnival (<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\" class=\"link\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/quote/CCL/\" data-i13n=\"cpos:8;pos:1\">CCL</a>), are soaring on eased US–Iran tensions.</p>",
